          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-10-16T18:00:55Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution expresses the sense of the Senate that (1) the Highway Trust Fund should achieve long-term solvency through user fees, and (2) any spending on federal highway programs during the next reauthorization period that exceeds current fund revenues and balances should be fully offset.</p>]]></text>
